and Gadducci, Fabio
and Lluch Lafuente, Alberto
and Vandin, Andrea",
editor="de Lara, Juan
and Zisman, Andrea",
title="A Conceptual Framework for Adaptation",
booktitle="Fundamental Approaches to Software Engineering",
